India’s Mukherjee Says No Decision on Raising Diesel, LPG Price

-- B y   A n o o p   A g r a w a l
-- 
2011-09-17T10:53:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-17/india-s-mukherjee-says-no-decision-on-raising-diesel-lpg-price.html
India  hasn’t yet decided on whether
to raise the cost of diesel, kerosene and liquified petroleum
gas after it raised petrol pump prices this week, Finance
Minister  Pranab Mukherjee  told reporters in Mumbai today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anoop Agrawal in Mumbai at 
